```python
def hoursForPaymentPlus10Hours(hourly, amount):
```

def puzzle_2():

It says Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday

There are a lot of unknown answers. We need to keep track of how many we buy and how many we did not sell

```bash
I sold 20 on Friday
I sold 5.5 on Monday
I sold 2 on Tuesday
I sold 65 on Thursday
I sold 10 on Wednesday
```

```yaml
days after Monday = 7
```

Now we must subtract to count how many we didn't sell
```yaml
Days we dont have:600
```

It must be the same number as days after Monday since we need to buy all 600

```yaml
Days to buy = 600 - (Days we don't have)
```

